Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.90,English,,0,0,0,,It was Christmas time, December of 1993,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:11.47,English,,0,0,0,,and there I was, just about to turn seven years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:15.79,English,,0,0,0,,and thoroughly transfixed by anything with a CPU inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:17.85,English,,0,0,0,,And luckily, the household my family was visiting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:21.98,English,,0,0,0,,for a Christmas party had a shiny new 486 in their office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.07,English,,0,0,0,,The guy who owned the computer was browsing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:26.39,English,,0,0,0,,and showing off the latest games he had downloaded
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:29.27,English,,0,0,0,,from a local BBS, like Halloween Harry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:31.14,English,,0,0,0,,and other platformers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:32.76,English,,0,0,0,,Then something happened
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:36.35,English,,0,0,0,,that changed my entire perception of video games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:38.41,English,,0,0,0,,I saw this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:43.18,English,,0,0,0,,I specifically remember him opening the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:45.95,English,,0,0,0,,shooting things until they collapsed in a bloody heap,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:48.69,English,,0,0,0,,and looking around at the green vats of slime,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:52.37,English,,0,0,0,,all in an environment that felt entirely believable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:55.82,English,,0,0,0,,It was textured, it had lighting, it was 3D,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:57.96,English,,0,0,0,,and just then my dad walked into the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:00:59.15,English,,0,0,0,,saw the gory carnage,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:02.71,English,,0,0,0,,and thought "ehh maybe this game isn't made for little kids."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:05.55,English,,0,0,0,,The dude on the computer apologized, shut it down,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:08.67,English,,0,0,0,,and let me play Commander Keen 4 instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.38,English,,0,0,0,,And while I was notably impressed by that as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.81,English,,0,0,0,,I never forgot that other game
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:16.10,English,,0,0,0,,with the green vats of slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:20.92,English,,0,0,0,,The guns, the demons, that feeling of doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:23.79,English,,0,0,0,,I thought about it every so often for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:26.36,English,,0,0,0,,those images burned into my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:28.36,English,,0,0,0,,It was not until many years later
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:30.77,English,,0,0,0,,in the days of peer-to-peer file sharing services
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.25,English,,0,0,0,,like Napster and Morpheus,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:34.90,English,,0,0,0,,that I finally got to play it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:38.18,English,,0,0,0,,I found some shady executable for Doom 95
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:40.16,English,,0,0,0,,and those memories came flooding back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:43.29,English,,0,0,0,,as I played through E1M1 for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.13,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd played games like Unreal and Thief at that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:47.03,English,,0,0,0,,but Doom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:48.71,English,,0,0,0,,It was still able to get its hooks into me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:50.43,English,,0,0,0,,with no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:52.61,English,,0,0,0,,The shooting, the music, the level design,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:54.93,English,,0,0,0,,the way enemies consistently surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:57.29,English,,0,0,0,,It felt shockingly fresh, even though the game
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:59.38,English,,0,0,0,,was eight years old at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:02.71,English,,0,0,0,,And now, with it approaching 23 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:05.75,English,,0,0,0,,and a new Doom looming on the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:10.03,English,,0,0,0,,it's finally time to discuss the one and only Doom,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:12.24,English,,0,0,0,,here on LGR.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:16.20,English,,0,0,0,,And yes, sometime later, I repented of my file sharing sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:18.23,English,,0,0,0,,Here's my personal copy of the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:20.88,English,,0,0,0,,which came in this slim cardboard sleeve
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.76,English,,0,0,0,,directly from id Software.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.66,English,,0,0,0,,Now, originally, Doom was a shareware game, meaning that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:27.81,English,,0,0,0,,there was a sizable chunk of it made available for free,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:30.62,English,,0,0,0,,including the level I saw as a seven year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:32.73,English,,0,0,0,,If you wanted the whole thing, and who didn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:35.52,English,,0,0,0,,you couldn't just go to a computer store and buy it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:38.69,English,,0,0,0,,you had to order it by phone or by mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:41.50,English,,0,0,0,,And when you did, they'd send you this package.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:44.50,English,,0,0,0,,That's why there's no barcode or anything like that on here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.57,English,,0,0,0,,it was never officially sold in stores,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:48.63,English,,0,0,0,,at least not in the U.S.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:52.24,English,,0,0,0,,You just got this little box, the game on some floppy disks,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:54.02,English,,0,0,0,,and a stapled together manual,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:57.20,English,,0,0,0,,which is of surprisingly decent quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:58.38,English,,0,0,0,,However, that's not to say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:02.02,English,,0,0,0,,that Doom was never, ever sold in American stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:03.36,English,,0,0,0,,Now for one thing, the shareware version
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:06.16,English,,0,0,0,,got all sorts of retail releases, including this one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.03,English,,0,0,0,,that was bundled alongside GT Software distributed games
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:11.32,English,,0,0,0,,like Wolfenstein 3D.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:13.04,English,,0,0,0,,The box looks a little more substantial
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.23,English,,0,0,0,,than the official full version release,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.17,English,,0,0,0,,but it's still just the shareware episode
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.25,English,,0,0,0,,that you could download for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.52,English,,0,0,0,,It wasn't until 1995 with the release
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:23.83,English,,0,0,0,,of The Ultimate Doom, that store shelves were graced
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:26.26,English,,0,0,0,,with the full version's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.61,English,,0,0,0,,The box art may not be as impressive as the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.93,English,,0,0,0,,but it included all the original episodes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.91,English,,0,0,0,,plus an additional fourth episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:37.14,English,,0,0,0,,and the latest patches, which made it an attractive option
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:39.73,English,,0,0,0,,for old and new players alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:42.62,English,,0,0,0,,There were also a slew of add-on packs for Doom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:45.68,English,,0,0,0,,like the omni-present D!Zone series of packs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.70,English,,0,0,0,,which added all sorts of maps and custom content.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:50.40,English,,0,0,0,,Also worth mentioning for collectors
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:54.01,English,,0,0,0,,is the Doom Collector's Edition, released in 2001.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.11,English,,0,0,0,,This has some pretty metal box art,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.13,English,,0,0,0,,and includes Final Doom, Ultimate Doom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.17,English,,0,0,0,,and the sequel, Doom II.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.46,English,,0,0,0,,But yeah, for the rest of the video,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:03.84,English,,0,0,0,,I'll just be taking a look at Doom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.54,English,,0,0,0,,and The Ultimate Doom, because I mean, ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.46,English,,0,0,0,,They make me moist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:11.75,English,,0,0,0,,And I'll probably explode if I don't play them again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:15.05,English,,0,0,0,,Doom begins with this fantastic splash screen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.69,English,,0,0,0,,and some appropriate mood setting MIDI music
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.57,English,,0,0,0,,by the magnificent, Maestro Bobby Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.32,English,,0,0,0,,While a demo plays in the background,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.41,English,,0,0,0,,you're free to peruse the options,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.40,English,,0,0,0,,look at registration information,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.46,English,,0,0,0,,or start up a game and dive into the depths of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.63,English,,0,0,0,,And since Hell is quite nice this time of year,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.70,English,,0,0,0,,I recommend choosing your difficulty and doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.16,English,,0,0,0,,Heh, and I always loved that nightmare difficulty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:47.87,English,,0,0,0,,is brutally honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:48.88,English,,0,0,0,,It's unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:51.47,English,,0,0,0,,No complaints if you play it, it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.85,English,,0,0,0,,Now I could very well talk about a hundred thousand topics
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:57.85,English,,0,0,0,,in regards to Doom from here forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.33,English,,0,0,0,,The creation story of the game is fascinating,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:02.75,English,,0,0,0,,the people behind its development are legendary,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:04.33,English,,0,0,0,,the tale of how it played a huge part
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.42,English,,0,0,0,,in creating the SRB is interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.52,English,,0,0,0,,the idea that its level design and weapons selection
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.37,English,,0,0,0,,are the daddy of all FPS games,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.26,English,,0,0,0,,and the fact that the technical feats
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:14.08,English,,0,0,0,,that this was pulling off in 1993
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:17.06,English,,0,0,0,,were like something from another world back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.80,English,,0,0,0,,but because each of those topics
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.54,English,,0,0,0,,deserve a video of their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:23.79,English,,0,0,0,,I just want to talk about the gameplay in general today
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.72,English,,0,0,0,,and how it makes me feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.30,English,,0,0,0,,Namely, there are a few things about Doom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.67,English,,0,0,0,,that make it distinctly Doom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:33.63,English,,0,0,0,,and nothing else has since compared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:36.16,English,,0,0,0,,Well, other than Doom II, which is arguably the better game
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.94,English,,0,0,0,,even though its more or less an add-on to this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:41.97,English,,0,0,0,,but that, too, is for another video another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.76,English,,0,0,0,,Ugh, man, isn't Doom too great?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.73,English,,0,0,0,,The new enemies, the phenomenal levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.59,English,,0,0,0,,the super shotgun, ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.08,English,,0,0,0,,Okay I'm sorry, I'm getting ahead of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.55,English,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.90,English,,0,0,0,,So what is it that makes Doom Doom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.97,English,,0,0,0,,Well for me, it's a combination of controls,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:59.01,English,,0,0,0,,level design, pacing, weapons, and atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:05:59.96,English,,0,0,0,,If any one of those were taken away,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.37,English,,0,0,0,,it would be another thing entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:03.98,English,,0,0,0,,Much like if you're mixing drinks
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:06.37,English,,0,0,0,,and leave out a key ingredient in one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.19,English,,0,0,0,,sure it's still more or less the same drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:09.44,English,,0,0,0,,but it's also different enough
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.69,English,,0,0,0,,that you may as well get another name entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:15.52,English,,0,0,0,,With Doom, that cocktail of control over your character,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.47,English,,0,0,0,,the layout, the features of each map,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.01,English,,0,0,0,,the expertly crafted speed and difficulty,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.19,English,,0,0,0,,the enjoyable lethal array of guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:25.06,English,,0,0,0,,and the overall feeling of exploring each level,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:26.64,English,,0,0,0,,all of these come together in a way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:28.81,English,,0,0,0,,that makes Doom distinct,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:32.68,English,,0,0,0,,and in my opinion is where the so-called Doom clones
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.95,English,,0,0,0,,of the mid-90s frequently fell short.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.76,English,,0,0,0,,When you're controlling Doom guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:39.93,English,,0,0,0,,as he is so creatively called,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:42.72,English,,0,0,0,,everything feels like it's in its place,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:46.28,English,,0,0,0,,like it has a purpose and nothing is extraneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.02,English,,0,0,0,,There's an intimate sense of connection
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:50.03,English,,0,0,0,,between your hands, the hardware,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:52.05,English,,0,0,0,,and what's happening on screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.49,English,,0,0,0,,It's like your keyboard and mouse transform
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.93,English,,0,0,0,,into a piece of finely tuned weaponry,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.16,English,,0,0,0,,one that's more than capable of wiping out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:02.51,English,,0,0,0,,the entirety of Hell's forces, if you're skilled enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:05.27,English,,0,0,0,,And you know, just when you think you've got the hang of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:07.58,English,,0,0,0,,repetition gives way to surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:10.48,English,,0,0,0,,as something you forgot was there catches you off guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:13.18,English,,0,0,0,,or something you didn't know was there kills you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.27,English,,0,0,0,,This leads right into the level design
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:18.26,English,,0,0,0,,which seems kind of nonsensical at first glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.61,English,,0,0,0,,I mean this is supposed to be a space military base
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:22.33,English,,0,0,0,,for the most part, and if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.08,English,,0,0,0,,they oughta fire their architect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.75,English,,0,0,0,,The number of dead ends, labyrinths, and secret doors
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.36,English,,0,0,0,,is downright bizarre in that respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:32.50,English,,0,0,0,,But what it lacks in logical believability,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.62,English,,0,0,0,,it makes up for in pure fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.81,English,,0,0,0,,Over two decades later, and the levels hold up in ways
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:42.31,English,,0,0,0,,that surprised me even more on playing through it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.71,English,,0,0,0,,It's a web of carefully constructed switches,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.53,English,,0,0,0,,windows, doors, passageways,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.73,English,,0,0,0,,secret areas, and floor toggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.63,English,,0,0,0,,And while each one is placed with an explicit purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:52.99,English,,0,0,0,,not all of them are there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.46,English,,0,0,0,,for every player on every play through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:57.46,English,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you want to do a speed run,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.00,English,,0,0,0,,sometimes you want to take it slow,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.22,English,,0,0,0,,other times you just want to search for secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:04.13,English,,0,0,0,,and beyond that you may want to go for a new record
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:07.07,English,,0,0,0,,in terms of items grabbed and enemies slaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:10.33,English,,0,0,0,,100 percenting the game is something I've never done,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:13.25,English,,0,0,0,,but the manner in which these levels are constructed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:16.27,English,,0,0,0,,makes me long to pull it off someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.66,English,,0,0,0,,And then seeing spots where Doom isn't afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.48,English,,0,0,0,,to do something crazy to the player,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.85,English,,0,0,0,,like tossing them into a strobe-lit dark room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.30,English,,0,0,0,,or instantly dropping them into a pit of demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.48,English,,0,0,0,,because they stepped on the wrong floor tile,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:31.15,English,,0,0,0,,makes me yearn for more first person shooters like this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.57,English,,0,0,0,,that didn't bother coddling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.79,English,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, the pacing of the game keeps you on edge
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:38.84,English,,0,0,0,,throughout the entire campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:41.58,English,,0,0,0,,From E1M1 onward, you're greeted with a game
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.20,English,,0,0,0,,that's simple to control, yet wickedly fast
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.84,English,,0,0,0,,and unafraid to dole out the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:50.53,English,,0,0,0,,Doom goes balls out in the way it tosses demons at you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:53.40,English,,0,0,0,,often from within areas that have since been termed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:56.28,English,,0,0,0,,monster closets, and if you can't see them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:09:00.43,English,,0,0,0,,you can hear them, and that compels you to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.23,English,,0,0,0,,To put it simply, if there's demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.14,English,,0,0,0,,you're probably going the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.07,English,,0,0,0,,And each enemy is designed in such a way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:08.08,English,,0,0,0,,that directly counters the moves and weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.71,English,,0,0,0,,you've gained thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:13.60,English,,0,0,0,,Some feature hit-scan weapons, others utilize projectiles
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:14.90,English,,0,0,0,,that can be dodged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.69,English,,0,0,0,,Several will chew your face off if you're too close,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:21.19,English,,0,0,0,,and others will compel you to use your most powerful weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:22.72,English,,0,0,0,,even if you're running low on ammo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.96,English,,0,0,0,,and probably should be saving up for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.37,English,,0,0,0,,But man, how hard is it to save up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:28.72,English,,0,0,0,,when the weapons are this good anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.92,English,,0,0,0,,Doom builds on the formula set forth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.27,English,,0,0,0,,in Wolfenstein 3D in so many ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.91,English,,0,0,0,,then bumps it up so many notches
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.95,English,,0,0,0,,that it's hard to even compare the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.00,English,,0,0,0,,Yet it's easy to lose sight of how legendary it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:43.69,English,,0,0,0,,seeing as practically first person shooter from here onward
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:47.25,English,,0,0,0,,has aped the basic Doom load-out to some degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:51.50,English,,0,0,0,,Punching for basic melee, a chainsaw for ballsy risktakers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.94,English,,0,0,0,,a pistol for when you're low on everything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:57.29,English,,0,0,0,,a shotgun because taking down multiple enemies is great,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:00.25,English,,0,0,0,,a chain-gun that puts the pistol ammo to good use,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:03.51,English,,0,0,0,,a rocket launcher for blowing things up including yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:06.76,English,,0,0,0,,a plasma gun for tearing through enemies at a rapid rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:09.93,English,,0,0,0,,and the one and only BFG 9000,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.46,English,,0,0,0,,the biggest [bleep] gun indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.35,English,,0,0,0,,Every one of these is a skillfully crafted tool
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:18.41,English,,0,0,0,,for dispatching violent justice on the Hell spawn
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.27,English,,0,0,0,,that roam the once hallowed halls
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:23.05,English,,0,0,0,,of wherever the hell this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:25.84,English,,0,0,0,,Once you figure out how to best use each gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.96,English,,0,0,0,,the fun never ends because you know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:31.04,English,,0,0,0,,that there's a proper time and place for every one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.94,English,,0,0,0,,and usually that place is dark, horrific,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:37.57,English,,0,0,0,,and downright delicious in its brooding sci-fi atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:41.13,English,,0,0,0,,The aesthetic of Doom is timeless if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.88,English,,0,0,0,,That happy little side effect of the game engine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.84,English,,0,0,0,,where everything was dark in the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.15,English,,0,0,0,,it's arguably the single most important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:51.76,English,,0,0,0,,for giving Doom its distinctive look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:53.17,English,,0,0,0,,Darkness is everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.55,English,,0,0,0,,only a few steps away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:57.28,English,,0,0,0,,Even in what appeared to be brightly lit rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.64,English,,0,0,0,,There is no hiding from it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:00.27,English,,0,0,0,,and it will probably tear your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:02.16,English,,0,0,0,,from your mortal form in no time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.47,English,,0,0,0,,unless you've got your trusty boom stick on hand
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.37,English,,0,0,0,,and in that case, keep the finger on the trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:08.46,English,,0,0,0,,and do not let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.72,English,,0,0,0,,Whether you're scouting out science facilities
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:13.19,English,,0,0,0,,or meandering around the halls of the damned,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:17.37,English,,0,0,0,,Doom's levels ooze style of the most dreadful variety.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:21.70,English,,0,0,0,,Yet, it's not as dark as its software's next game, Quake,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.08,English,,0,0,0,,it's still got that bright dash
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:26.19,English,,0,0,0,,of delightfully pixelated color here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:28.70,English,,0,0,0,,If only to remind you that what you're fighting for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.50,English,,0,0,0,,is probably worth it, and it's the early 90s.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:34.23,English,,0,0,0,,Bright colors are still cool in video games.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:35.73,English,,0,0,0,,And every so often, you'll run into something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:39.35,English,,0,0,0,,that the devout of the time took much offense to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:41.37,English,,0,0,0,,Upside down crosses, pentagrams,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:44.83,English,,0,0,0,,images of demons and various other bits of Satanic imagery
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.51,English,,0,0,0,,that really nailed down the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:48.92,English,,0,0,0,,that Doom is pretty freaking metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:51.01,English,,0,0,0,,I'm not just talking about the design of things either,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:54.40,English,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about that stellar soundtrack by Bobby Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:06.69,English,,0,0,0,,Sure, much of it mimics the songs of Metallica, Pantera,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.57,English,,0,0,0,,Slayer, and Judas Priest, but I say bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:11.39,English,,0,0,0,,This is a game that was clearly made by
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:15.62,English,,0,0,0,,100% all natural geeks fueled by copious metal albums,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:19.36,English,,0,0,0,,soft drinks, leftover pizza, and D&D campaigns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:21.32,English,,0,0,0,,Doom is an interactive monument
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.48,English,,0,0,0,,to early 90s popular culture and more specifically,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:27.53,English,,0,0,0,,the culture of dorks who just like the sound of hard rock
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:30.57,English,,0,0,0,,and the sight of blood and guts on a computer screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:32.40,English,,0,0,0,,my kind of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.71,English,,0,0,0,,But beyond how enjoyable it is to play,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.37,English,,0,0,0,,how influential it was on gaming,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.42,English,,0,0,0,,and how unique it was to stick in my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.32,English,,0,0,0,,for all those years as a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:43.63,English,,0,0,0,,Doom is about much more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:46.33,English,,0,0,0,,Doom is all about its community.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.77,English,,0,0,0,,The culture of creativity that this game inspired
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:50.15,English,,0,0,0,,is the stuff of legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.40,English,,0,0,0,,And the crazy thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.90,English,,0,0,0,,it wasn't even released with modding tools,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.70,English,,0,0,0,,yet immediately after the release of the shareware episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:59.29,English,,0,0,0,,players of the game got to work on creating utilities
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.15,English,,0,0,0,,that allowed users to mod the game
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.61,English,,0,0,0,,into practically whatever they wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:06.42,English,,0,0,0,,Chances are, If you've given much of your time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.98,English,,0,0,0,,to Doom at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.76,English,,0,0,0,,you've given some time to trying out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.34,English,,0,0,0,,or making your own custom WAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:15.86,English,,0,0,0,,Simpsons Doom, Star Wars Doom, Back to Saturn X,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.91,English,,0,0,0,,Kill Barney, on and on and on and on,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:20.95,English,,0,0,0,,and to this day, there are still tons of them being made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.58,English,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but source ports, total conversions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.96,English,,0,0,0,,and modding overhauls, have transformed Doom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:28.57,English,,0,0,0,,into things that are absolutely mindblowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.97,English,,0,0,0,,Not to mention met with mainstream success,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:34.02,English,,0,0,0,,who hasn't heard of Brutal Doom at this point, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:36.01,English,,0,0,0,,And it's not just the excellent single-player
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.72,English,,0,0,0,,that got so many people modding the game either,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:41.35,English,,0,0,0,,it was the included multiplayer modes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.15,English,,0,0,0,,These not only let several players
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.57,English,,0,0,0,,go through the entire campaign cooperatively,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.80,English,,0,0,0,,but they could also compete
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.40,English,,0,0,0,,in what the game called deathmatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:53.23,English,,0,0,0,,Yep, you've got Doom to thank for cementing the popularity
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:55.91,English,,0,0,0,,of this mode that is still incredibly popular
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.18,English,,0,0,0,,in multiplayer shooters to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:01.14,English,,0,0,0,,It's a testament to Doom's original gameplay
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:03.66,English,,0,0,0,,that got people that enthusiastic about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:05.39,English,,0,0,0,,So much so, that their enthusiasm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.70,English,,0,0,0,,turned into a rich creative outlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.33,English,,0,0,0,,And seeing as that outlet has turned many a modder
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:12.35,English,,0,0,0,,into a professional game developer,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:16.61,English,,0,0,0,,the influence Doom has had is, well it's hard to fathom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:18.99,English,,0,0,0,,And that's why I have to talk about it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:22.18,English,,0,0,0,,and will be talking about it for years in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:26.74,English,,0,0,0,,However Doom 2016 turns out, well frankly I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.70,English,,0,0,0,,I'll play it, I hope I enjoy it, but either way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.88,English,,0,0,0,,it doesn't change how I'll feel about all I've just said
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.25,English,,0,0,0,,in this video.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.79,English,,0,0,0,,Regardless of where Doom's legacy ends up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.34,English,,0,0,0,,in Bethesda's hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:42.03,English,,0,0,0,,it's the original Doom games that still have my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:44.58,English,,0,0,0,,Or more aptly, my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,记得那是1993的圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:11.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我当时也就差不多七岁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:15.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且对任何有CPU的东西都十分感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:17.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,幸运的是，我当时去开圣诞派对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:21.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,的人家书房里有台全新的486电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:26.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当时那位正在玩电脑的大哥正在浏览，并向我显摆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:31.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从当地BBS下载的游戏，诸如Halloween Harry之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:36.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后那个改变我对游戏看法的事情就发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:38.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我看到了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:43.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我十分清晰地记得他打开了那扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:45.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,打着怪兽，直到它们倒在血泊中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:48.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后看着周围的绿色毒河
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:52.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个画面合在一处，让人难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:55.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这玩意有纹理！这玩意有光照！这玩意是3D的！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:57.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就在那时我老爹走进了屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:00:59.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看着屏幕上的血流漂橹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:02.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后说：“额，这游戏小孩玩不合适吧。”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:05.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那位玩电脑的大哥道了歉，把游戏关了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:08.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后就让我玩Commmander Keen 4
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然这个游戏也挺耐人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:16.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我永远忘不了那个流着绿色毒河的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:20.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那些枪声不断，怪兽吓人，毁灭一切的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:23.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那游戏的画面几年来一直在我的脑海里挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:26.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并在我的心中留下了烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:30.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,几年后，趁着那时P2P网络正火之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,例如Napster和Morpheus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.25,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：在中国是迅雷，QQ旋风等，吸着eMule和BitTorrent的血。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:34.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我终于搞来了一份来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:38.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我当时下载了一份来路可疑的DOOM 95程序
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:40.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后当我第一次亲自玩第一章第一关时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:43.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一个个鲜活的面容又在我眼前飞扬了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的，我当时像个小偷一样的玩游戏，心里很虚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:47.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是《毁灭战士》呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:50.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它还是毫无疑问地把我给迷住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:52.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它射击的方式，它富有激情的BGM，它精巧的关卡设计
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:54.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,源源不断的地狱渣子让我印象深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:59.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就算当时游戏发行了八年，我玩起来还是觉得恐怖又新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:02.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在呢，这个游戏已经23岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:05.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且全新的《毁灭战士》又将发行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:10.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在终于是时候来谈论这独一无二的《毁灭战士》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:12.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在我的LGR频道上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:16.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，在这之后，我也为我盗版玩游戏而后悔:-(
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:16.20,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：各位在网上听歌的，也许你听到的就是盗版，{\fnComic Sans MS}av711540711@Pig_Floyd
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:18.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是我自己买的游戏拷贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:20.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,装在这个超薄的纸盒中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,直接从开发商id Software发货
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，最初的《毁灭战士》是个共享软件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.66,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：共享软件是各种”先使用后付费“的软件，诸如WinRAR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:27.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,意味着你可以从很多中渠道搞到免费版本游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:30.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,包括我七岁时看到的关卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:32.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你想玩所有关卡的话，而且谁不想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:35.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你想当然地去电脑城买
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:38.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你必须经由电话或者邮件去订购
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:41.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当你订购完成后，你会收到个包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:44.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么这上面没有条码之类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这玩意从来就没有在商场里卖过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:48.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,至少在美国是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:52.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你只是搞来了这个小盒子，一堆装着游戏的磁盘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:57.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有这装订好的游戏说明书，而且质量出奇的好:-)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:03:02.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，这也不代表在美国没卖过《毁灭战士》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:03.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,顺便一提，这个免费版本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:06.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,倒是在市面上能见到，包括这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:11.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,附带于其他GT Software发行的游戏中的，诸如德军总部3D
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:15.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个相比完整版的，看上去更加充实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:19.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是里面仍然是免费版游戏，你在网上可以免费下载
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:26.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,直到1995年《毁灭战士终极版》的发行，商场架子上才看见完整版的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也许盒子上的画没有别的游戏的吸引人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是它包括了原先完整版的所有关卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且还附带了第四章
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:37.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有最新的游戏补丁，这个让
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:39.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,新老玩家都很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:42.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,之后还有一连串的毁灭战士附加包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:45.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,诸如omni-presentD!Zone系列附加包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,里面包括了一系列的地图和自制内容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:50.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对于收藏家来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:54.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个2001年发行的《毁灭战士典藏版》也值得收藏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,盒子设计得十分金属
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还包括了《最终毁灭战士》, 《终极毁灭战士》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以及续集，《毁灭战士二代》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，接下来的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:03.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们只是来讨论原版《毁灭战士》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以及《终极毁灭战士》，因为它们......
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们使我感动至极
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:11.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,要是我三天不碰，我估计又得踢坏太上老君的炼丹炉了:-P
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:15.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《毁灭战士》由这个超级耐人的开屏动画开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,伴随着十分能调动情绪的MIDI音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,由音乐大师Bobby Prince编曲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当游戏演示在背景展示时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以自由地浏览这些选项
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看一下授权情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者开局游戏，打入阴曹地府的核心B-)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,鉴于现在地狱的各位都十分儒雅随和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我十分建议大家挑个合适难度来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且呢，我十分喜欢的噩梦难度（超级难的难度）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:47.37,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：第一和第五个难度子弹加倍，但是第五个难度怪兽攻击性更强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:47.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\pos(1722,804)}我是个宝宝\N\N简单点行吗\N\N我准备好了\N\N超级恐怖\N\N噩梦到死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:47.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对你而言就很难了:-(
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:48.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这对你可能不太公平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:51.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你要玩的话，出事别怪人哦:-|
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:51.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,458)\fs60}你确定要玩这个难度吗？\N难道你很喜欢被虐吗？\N{\fs35}（这个难度甚至没那么的公平）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:57.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从现在开始我可以滔滔不绝地讨论关于毁灭战士的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个游戏的幕后故事也十分有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:02.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,开发游戏的大师们，个个都是传奇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:06.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们在开发SRB时的巨大贡献十分有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们的关卡设计和武器设定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是目前所有FPS游戏的基础
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:14.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有不得不说的，在1993年超前的技术壮举
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:17.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在当时就好象曹操看见袁绍营里吃着玉米
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:20.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但鉴于上述细节都适合做个节目细谈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:23.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我今天只是来大概谈谈游戏的玩法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以及它给我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，《毁灭战士》肯定有些特点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,才让其称上”毁灭“二字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fs105\pos(990,300)}还不仅仅是“毁灭”哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:30.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1312,146)\fs105}这可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:33.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且在之前从来没有出现过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:36.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，抛开《毁灭战士二代》，当然也是个好的续作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,尽管这个或多或少算是《毁灭战士》的DLC
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:41.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是这个呢，还是回来再做个视频吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Emmm，难道二代不耐人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,全新的敌人，加强的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有双管猎枪，啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，刚才失态，请见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一手的满足:-)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么是什么让《毁灭战士》担当得起“毁灭”二字呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对于我来说，这是由控制方式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:59.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,关卡设计，关卡衔接（原意走步），武器，还有氛围来决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:05:59.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,要是缺少了一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那就是另一个特点了，甚至于另一种游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:03.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就像你认为林妹妹说话很扎人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:06.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是你忘了她的小姐身份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然这还是个有血有肉的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:09.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是和一开始想的完全不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这可能就是另一个人了，比如晴雯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:11.69,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：原文意思是调饮料忘了最重要的调料，以至于这杯饮料不是你所想要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:15.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当你玩《毁灭战士》的时候，你会感到那种控制角色的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,整个游戏的界面，每张地图的各个机关
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有精心设计的速度和难度，这些感觉都杂糅在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,令人愉悦的枪林弹雨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:25.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有探索每一关时的无所适从和提心吊胆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:26.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些感觉的集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:28.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,造就了这个游戏的“毁灭特色”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:32.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在我看来，这也就让那些90年代中期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,流行的类《毁灭战士》游戏都黯然失色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当你在控制毁灭战士这个人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:39.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大家都喜欢这么叫它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:42.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,很多事情看起来都各归其位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:46.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好像什么东西都是有前因后果，而不是外来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看上去他好像与你的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:50.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你的硬件，和屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:52.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,的一举一动都有很紧密的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就好像你的键盘和鼠标都穿越到游戏中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,变成了上膛的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且十分适合将地狱大军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:02.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,都给揍回他的老巢，只要你技巧足够熟练的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:05.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且你也知道，当你认为你解决得差不多时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:07.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,重复杀戮就变成了惊喜杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:10.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为一点疏忽就能让你喝上一壶的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:13.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者你没看见的敌人正在磨你的血:-(
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是精巧的关卡设计所带来的好处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:18.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,第一眼看上去有点无厘头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我的意思是说，这本应是个太空军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.61,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：{\fnComic Sans MS\fs60}UAC=Union Aerospace Corporation {\fn文泉驿等宽微米黑}联合太空技术集团
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:22.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,至少大部分区域都是这样的，真是如此的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,为啥不一把火给烧了呢:-P
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,杀掉的敌人数目，迷宫和秘密的门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些从头到尾都是无厘头的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:32.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,尽管这游戏细想想真是扯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,玩起来还是十分刺激的:-D
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,谁能想到20年后，这些设计精巧的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:42.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,关卡依然能让我惊奇不已，玩味不止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,各个关卡本身就是开关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,窗户，大门，过道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,秘密区域和楼梯开关的集合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后当每一个机关都各居其所时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:55.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,玩家们又不一定非得把它们都过一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:57.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有时你想速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有时你想驻足厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，你只是想搜索秘密地带
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:04.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,更有甚者，你只是想在捡完所有物品，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:07.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,杀掉所有敌人的情况下，看看自己是不是破了记录
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:10.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,集齐这个游戏所有关卡的的三个100%，我好像永远完不成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:10.33,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：KILLS 杀戮，ITEMS 物品，SECRETS 秘密地带
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:13.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是这些关卡精巧的设定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:16.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也让我能一直很高兴地卡在这一关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后看看那些能把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,毁灭战士给吓死的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,例如走进了一闪一闪昏暗的屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者很快就掉进装满了魔鬼的坑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为他走进了错误的楼梯:-(
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:33.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些都更让我对这种主动吓人的第一人称射击游戏更加喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,说到这个，这个游戏的节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:38.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,自始至终都是一样的逼人甚紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:41.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从第一章第一关开始，你所面对的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,易于操控，然而却是邪恶的快节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并毫不畏惧地向你抛出痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:50.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个游戏会源源不断地向你抛出一个个狼与豺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:53.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,经常是从你拿完东西后从哪堵墙后面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:56.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,突然冒出来的:-(，如果你看不见它们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:09:00.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以听见它们的狂吟，而这些迫使你继续走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,简单来说，怪物多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,八成就是准道儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且每一种怪兽都是按照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:08.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能用你目前能得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,武器所能解决掉的路子来设计的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:14.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有些怪兽有连击武器，有些怪兽你可以躲过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有些怪物呢呢，当你离它很近时，受到的伤害会很大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:21.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有些腻味人的会迫使你用最强力的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:22.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就算你弹量不足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且你也想在后面的战斗中节省些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是老弟啊，要是你也有一堆美式装备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:28.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你难道还会精打细算吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:33.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《毁灭战士》和《德军总部3D》在许多方面的设计语言是相似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:36.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后在此基础上提升很多，甚至比前者不知道高到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是大家还是没能意识到这个游戏的经典之处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:43.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只是片面地认为它是第一人称射击游戏的开山制作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:47.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,某种程度上给《毁灭战士》造成影响（没看懂，有懂的弹幕覆盖）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:51.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,用拳头来打群架，拿锯子砍掉那腻味人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,实在啥都没有的话，用手枪应急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:57.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,用猎枪来个一枪多头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:00.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,用机关枪来充分利用手枪子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:03.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,用火箭发射器来轰掉一切，包括自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:06.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,用等离子枪来灭掉能跑过记者的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:09.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，我们无法忘怀那唯一的BFG 9000
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,又大(big)又＊*（fxxking）的终极武器！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.46,Comments,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs55}Jensen Huang: 3090 is a beast, a ferocious GPU, a BFGPU
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每件武器都是精心设计的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:18.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,用来在地狱里用血和子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,宣扬我们人类暴力的一面，消灭它们的母巢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:23.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,正如它们玷污我们的神庙一样，并且把地狱翻个底朝天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:25.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当你搞明白如何正确使用每一种枪时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,杀戮的快感就永不停歇，因为你明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:31.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是这种武器在这个场合下的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一般来说，这种地方是十分黑暗，恐怖的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:37.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,正中这个游戏阴暗的科幻气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:41.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而这就是这个游戏在审美方面的成就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个游戏引擎一个比较好的方面是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,黑暗部分在很远就能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个在《毁灭战士》塑造形象方面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:51.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,显然是十分重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:53.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,黑暗无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也许就在几步之外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:57.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就算在看上去都是很亮的屋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,总会有什么东西藏在墙的后面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:02.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且会很快地把你的魂儿吓出来，并剁成齑粉:-(
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,除非你紧紧地握着你最信赖的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:08.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以以防万一，按住扳机，别让它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,无论你是在探索科学基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:13.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或是下了十八层地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:17.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《毁灭战士》怪异的关卡中流露出一股可怕的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:21.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，这个没有这个公司出的下一款游戏《雷神之锤》黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:26.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个游戏还是到处还是充满着鲜艳的像素和贴色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:28.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你能明白你在干什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个游戏很适合你，而且这可是90年代早期出品的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:34.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,鲜艳的颜色仍然在游戏界流行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:35.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且或多或少，你在遇到某些难过的机关时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:39.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你都得十分专心地解决它们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:41.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,倒五角星啊，神秘五角星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:44.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,恶魔的图片和一堆其他的撒旦图片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这也更加显示出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:48.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《毁灭战士》十分金属的内核
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:51.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，我说到不是设计还是啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:54.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我说到是Bobby Prince编的游戏音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:06.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，这些配乐大多受 Metallica, Pantera,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Slayer 和 Judas Priest 的影响，但是要我说，上劲就行！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:09.57,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：E1M8（第一章的最后一关）配乐的riff改编自 King Crimson 的 Starless
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:11.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些游戏显然是由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:15.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,100%纯极客在金属音乐的薰陶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:19.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,汽水和外卖披萨的满足和恐怖派对游戏的刺激下完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:21.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《毁灭战士》很明显是90年代早期西方流行文化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,的生动体现，主要是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:27.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那堆只想着听着重金属摇头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:30.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看着屏幕上血肉飞溅的小年轻们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:32.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没错，就是我们这样的人B-)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是咱先抛开玩游戏的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它在游戏史上的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:40.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以及它自我小时候以来给我的印象来接着说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:43.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《毁灭战士》可不止这些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:46.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《毁灭战士》有自己的圈子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:50.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,由这个游戏引出的创造力和同人也造就了这个游戏的传奇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:53.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,更令人疯狂的是，官方都没有发行过创造工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就在免费版本游戏发行后不长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:13:03.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,硬核玩家们就努力开发工具，让人们随意修改游戏，各显神通
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:07.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,万事俱备，你只要有足够的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你就可以装几个玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者自己定制WAD（Doom游戏引擎数据文件）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:15.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Simpsons Doom, Star Wars Doom, Back to Saturn X,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Kill Barney, 还有很多很多......
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:20.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且直到现在，还在有人做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不仅这些，还有源码修改，在线对话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.58,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：DOOM引擎（idTech 1）Linux版在1997-12-23开源，{\fnComic Sans MS\fs60}github id-Software/DOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,和深入定制，这些都把《毁灭战士》
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:28.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,变成了十分烧脑的橡皮泥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然它在主流市场的成功就更不必说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:34.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,毕竟有谁没听说过Brutal Doom（十分著名的DOOM Mod）呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:38.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且你不仅可以和别人一起为单人游戏搞Mod
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:41.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个游戏还有多人游戏模式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:45.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个不仅可以让梁山一百单八将们一起打战役
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:49.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且还可以在Deathmatch（死亡游戏）中来个三国并立
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:53.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的，你得感谢《毁灭战士》的多人游戏流行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:55.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,才让现在的多人射击游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能够继续流行，并不断壮大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:01.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是啊，《毁灭战士》奠基下的游戏方式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:03.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,让人们对此是如此的欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:05.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如此下去，它们的兴趣与激情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就转化为了无尽的创造力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后这无尽的创造力就让一个个写Mod的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:12.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,进化为专业的游戏开发者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:16.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《毁灭战士》的影响可真是......难以估量了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:18.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这也就是为什么我现在一直在谈论它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:22.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且在将来还会一直谈论它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:26.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然而Doom 2016版发行了，说真的，我对此并不太上心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:26.74,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：2016年5月13日在Steam上发行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我当然会玩它，并好好享受它，但是抛开这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:34.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它不会改变我刚才说到的，我对这个游戏的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:38.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不管《毁灭战士》系列在Bethesda（发行商）手里会变得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:42.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,原版《毁灭战士》游戏永远在我的心中有一席之地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:44.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,更准确地说，是我的心中:-)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0200F2&\pos(950,832)}结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:45.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0200F2&\pos(950,832)}结束了吗？
